text: DWNP (106.5 FM), broadcasting as 106.5 UMFM, is a radio station owned and operated by Multipoint Broadcasting Network. The station's studio and transmitter are located in Palayan.106.5 UMFM, pormal nang ipinakilala sa mga tagapakinig ==References== Category:Radio stations in Nueva Ecija Category:Radio stations established in 2017
